long paddock
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:grass on the sides of roads, often grazed by stock.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:between the fences; long acre
